OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Fwill affect the north and west of
OL,7,FScotland overnight, reaching Northern
OL,8,FIreland later. Turning breezy here
OL,9,Ftoo. Elsewhere it will be generally
OL,10,Fdry with clear spells. Patches of low
OL,11,Fcloud and fog forming in the lighter
OL,12,Fwinds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FPatchy rain will affect some
OL,15,Fnorthwestern areas during the morning,
OL,16,Fahead of some more persistent rain
OL,17,Farriving here later. Generally fine
OL,18,Felsewhere with some very warm, locally
OL,19,Fhot sunshine developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
